In re Resignation of Sheard.

[Cite as In re Resignation of Sheard (1991), 59 Ohio St. 3d 602.]

(No. 91-596 Submitted April 9, 1991 Decided April 17, 1991.)

The resignation of Gilbert A. Sheard as an attorney is accepted.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur.
